WEBVTT

00:00.560 --> 00:01.560
Your sister is right

00:01.760 --> 00:02.640
The sages said

00:02.800 --> 00:04.520
When Heaven is about to place a great responsibility on a person

00:04.760 --> 00:05.960
It first tests their resolve

00:05.960 --> 00:06.800
Exhausts their body

00:06.800 --> 00:07.800
And starves their flesh

00:08.800 --> 00:09.760
Following General Zu Kun

00:09.840 --> 00:10.560
Will be greatly beneficial

00:10.960 --> 00:11.560
For your future

00:12.360 --> 00:13.240
Then I'd still rather

00:13.480 --> 00:14.640
Follow sister and brother-in-law

00:14.800 --> 00:15.640
As a follower

00:16.080 --> 00:17.960
Why be a sage when I can be fine as is?

00:19.800 --> 00:20.320
Right

00:20.760 --> 00:22.200
Almost forgot the important matter
